  Database Configuration
  ==========================
  spring.datasource.url=jdbc:mysql://localhost:3306/sports_betting_db?useSSL=false&serverTimezone=UTC&allowPublicKeyRetrieval=true
  spring.datasource.username=YOUR_DATABASE_USERNAME
  spring.datasource.password=YOUR_DATABASE_PASSWORD
  spring.datasource.driver-class-name=com.mysql.cj.jdbc.Driver

  JPA / Hibernate
  spring.jpa.hibernate.ddl-auto=update
  spring.jpa.show-sql=false
  spring.jpa.properties.hibernate.dialect=org.hibernate.dialect.MySQLDialect

  ==========================
  Security Configuration (JWT)
  ==========================
  Generate a secure random string (at least 64 characters)
  grzechuhehe.app.jwtSecret=YOUR_VERY_LONG_SECRET_KEY_FOR_JWT_SIGNING_MIN_64_CHARS
  grzechuhehe.app.jwtExpirationMs=86400000

  ==========================
  Server Configuration
  ==========================
  server.port=8443

  SSL Configuration (Optional but recommended)
  server.ssl.key-store=classpath:keystore.p12
  server.ssl.key-store-password=your_keystore_password
  server.ssl.key-store-type=PKCS12
  server.ssl.key-alias=tomcat

  ==========================
  Logging
  ==========================
  logging.level.org.springframework.security=INFO
  logging.level.com.grzechuhehe.SportsBettingManagerApp=DEBUG

  ==========================
  File Uploads (If applicable)
  ==========================
  spring.servlet.multipart.max-file-size=2MB
  spring.servlet.multipart.max-request-size=2MB
